latestIgtvVideos.title: EASY SMOKEY EYES 🤎🖤
DEWY SUMMER GLAM ✨💜
HOW TO ALWAYS LOOK PUT TOGETHER ?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here, I have shown you ways in which you can look classy & chic m in no time with minimal wardrobe.
Few basic things to keep in mind when you want to achieve a put together look:
1. Always wear ironed & crisp clothes, no matter what. It can make any outfit look better.
2. Make sure you have clean nails. Does not matter, if you have long nails or short. It helps in presenting you well
3. You must smell good. Brush your teeth twice a day, spray good perfume/mist. No body wants to smell bad, right ?
4. Polished heels/shoes are a must. 
5. Wear a watch, it’s a timeless accessory. Also, opt for a chain watch rather a leather strap. It looks more chic.
6. Heels should be your first option. It goes with everything and it’s not necessary you always have to buy high pointed heels. You can buy low length block heels/strap heels. They look great and are so comfortable.
7. Invest in good basics, they go a long way and can be paired with everything. 
8. If not sure about your style, DO NOT EXPERIMENT with colour blocking. They can ruin your look and make you feel uncomfortable. Rather go for monochrome, or any neutral colour clothes as they are  effortless and looks stunning.
9. Don’t follow TRENDS all the time. For example: MID-RIFF flossing, if you don’t like it skip it. 
10. Buy classy cotton shirts & wide loose bottoms. They look super chic. You will thank me later. 

If you liked this video and found it helpful, please like/comment/share/save. It would mean so much. Thank you. 
I will see you in my next video. 
Much Love ✨
